gov.usgs.anss.seed

Class MiniSeedPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.seed.MiniSeedPool

  • public class MiniSeedPool
extends java.lang.Object
    This class forms a pool of miniseed blocks which can be allocated and freed, but not run through the garbage collector. Used mainly in CWBQuery so blocks are not constantly built into new MiniSeed objects and them reaped.
